<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
<title><%=title%></title>
<%- include('./partials/head'); %>
<style>
  .customcard {
    border:none;
    padding: 10px 50px;
  }
  .customcard::after {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0;
    -webkit-transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
    transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
  }
  .customcard:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02, 1.02);
    -webkit-transform: scale(1.02, 1.02);
    backface-visibility: hidden; 
    will-change: transform;
    box-shadow: 0 1rem 3rem rgba(0,0,0,.75) !important;
  }
  .customcard:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .customcard:hover .btn-outline-primary{
    color:white;
    background:#007bff;
  }

  .spendenteaser {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .spendenteaser__teaserText {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  .spendenteaser__link {
    background-color: white;
  }


</style>
</head>
<body class="container-fluid">

<header>
  <%- include('./partials/header'); %>

</header>


<main>
  
<div class="jumbotron">
    
    <div id="carouselExampleDark" class="carousel carousel-dark slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="10000">
          <a href="http://localhost:3000/products/search/630cfd376f9b74650d8821b9"><img src="https://www.unicef.org/sites/default/files/styles/hero_extended/public/UN0691098%20%281%29_0.jpg?itok=WNLpnlfK" width="450" height="620" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." >
          </a>
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="2000">
          <img src="https://global.unitednations.entermediadb.net/assets/mediadb/services/module/asset/downloads/preset/Libraries/Production+Library/02-09-2022-UNICEF-UN0696539-Pakistan.jpg/image1170x530cropped.jpg"  width="450" height="620" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <br>
            <br>
            <h5></h5>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1242803826-1.jpg?w=1500" width="450" height="620" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
           <a href=""></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>      
    </div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="card text-center">
              
      <div class="card-body ">
        <hr class="my-4">
        <h4 class="card-title text-dark ">Conflict, food shortages, and, climate crises have left a record 33 million people in critical need.</h4>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p class="card-text">An urgent need for funding has arisen to address critical issues plaguing communities, particularly those suffering from illnesses, malnutrition, and inadequate access to medical services. The situation demands immediate attention as countless lives are at stake. Insufficient resources have left many individuals vulnerable to debilitating diseases, exacerbating their suffering and jeopardizing their chances of survival. Moreover, malnutrition continues to afflict a significant portion of the population, leading to weakened immune systems and heightened susceptibility to various health conditions. Without intervention, the cycle of illness and malnutrition perpetuates, resulting in a devastating toll on communities' overall well-being.</p>
        
       
      </div>
    
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="card">
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="spendenteaser bg-success text-white p-3">
      <i class="fa fa-heart fa-3x spendenteaser__heart text-green"></i>

      <div class="spendenteaser__teaserText">
        <p class="mt-1" style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Help the people affected by the disasters with your donation</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/donation" title="Donate now!" target="_top" class="btn btn-lg btn-success text-success spendenteaser__link">Donate now</a>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>
 
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-body">
<div class="card-title">
  <h4 class="card-header text-primary text-center">Campaigns for the change</h4>

</div>
   
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="images/o1.jpg" alt="Flood Donation">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Flood Donation</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Support those affected by floods with your generous donations.</p>
                <a href="/flooddonation" class="btn btn-success">Donate</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
    
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="images/o2.jpg" alt="Earthquake Donation">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Earthquake Donation</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Help the victims of earthquakes by contributing to the relief efforts.</p>
                <a href="/earthquakedonation" class="btn btn-success">Donate</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
    
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="images/o3.jpg" alt="Dessert Water Donation">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Desert Water Donation</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Provide clean drinking water to arid regions and help combat water scarcity.</p>
                <a href="/waterplantdonation" class="btn btn-success">Donate</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


    
    <div class="card text-center">
    
      <div class="card-body ">
    
        <h5 class="card-title text-dark">Current situation</h5>
        <p class="card-text">People are facing many challenges in the informal settlements, camped along roadsides to escape surrounding flood waters, setting up shelters with whatever resources they have</p>
        <div class="row ml-3 mt-4 ">


          <% posts.forEach(function(post) { %>
            <div class="col-lg-3">
              <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-12 mt-4 mb-sm-4">
                <div class="card img-hover-zoom--quick-zoom " style="width: 18rem;">
                  <img src="/uploads/blogimages/<%=post.image1%>" class="card-img-top " alt="...">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-dark"><%=post.title.substring(0,55) + "..."%></h5>
                    <p class="card-text"><%=post.description.substring(0,85) + "..."%></p>
                    <a href="/posts/viewnewspost/<%= post._id%>"> <button type="button" style="border-radius:30px"class="btn  btn-outline-secondary btn-sm px-3 me-2 fw-semibold" >
                      Read news
                    </button></a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
         
           
          <% }); %>
          
          
          
 
        </div>
        <br>
        <a href="/posts/floodnews"> <button type="button" style="border-radius:30px"class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm px-3 me-2 fw-semibold" >
          Browse more
        </button></a>
       
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer text-muted">
        2 days ago
      </div>

      
    </div>
    
    
   
</div>


    

 
</main>

<footer>
  <%- include('./partials/footer'); %>
</footer>

</body>


</html>